      <title>农民为何担心长期护理的成本</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/09/03/nx-s1-5096814/why-farmers-worry-about-the-costs-of-long-term-care</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农民往往“土地富，钱少”。那些需要养老院护理的人可能不得不卖掉或拆散他们的农场来支付养老院护理的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/09/03/nx-s1-5096814/why-farmers-worry-about-the-costs-of-long-term-care</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:10:58 GMT</pubDate>
